### Get all blog posts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Accept: application/json

###

### Create new blog post - Success (make sure user with ID 1 exists first)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first blog post. It talks about Spring Boot and AOP.",
  "authorId": 1
}

###

